interface:
payable main contract AensMarketContact =
  record state = {names_owner : map(string, address),names_order : map(string, AensMarketContact.order),names_record : map(address, list(AensMarketContact.order)),config : AensMarketContact.config}
  record order = {name : string,old_owner : address,new_owner : address,start_amount : int,left_amount : int,current_amount : int,all_bonus_fee : int,start_height : int,over_height : int,premium_count : int}
  record config = {max_order_height : int,decimals : int,bonus_fee : int,platform_fee : int,foundation_fee : int,platform_address : address,foundation_address : address,delay_height : int,record_max_count : int,length_multiple : int,min_premium_percentage : int}
  record fees = {platform : int,foundation : int,amount : int}
  stateful entrypoint init : () => AensMarketContact.state
  payable stateful entrypoint put_name : (string, signature, int, int) => unit
  stateful entrypoint revoked_name : (string) => unit
  payable stateful entrypoint raise_name : (string) => unit
  stateful entrypoint deal_name : (string) => unit
  entrypoint get_names_order : () => map(string, AensMarketContact.order)
  entrypoint get_name_order : (string) => AensMarketContact.order
  entrypoint get_name_records : (address) => list(AensMarketContact.order)
  entrypoint get_name_next_raise_price : (int) => int
  entrypoint get_name_fee : (int) => AensMarketContact.fees
  entrypoint get_name_max_price : (string) => int
  entrypoint format_name_length_price : (int) => int
  stateful entrypoint update_config : (AensMarketContact.config) => unit
  stateful entrypoint receive_name_admin : (string) => unit
  stateful entrypoint receive_balance_admin : (string) => unit
  entrypoint get_state : () => AensMarketContact.state
